## PART 6 — 90-Day Ranking Roadmap

### Month 1 — Foundation & Indexing (Weeks 1–4)

**Technical Fixes (Week 1 — do these first):**
- [ ] Fix `robots.txt` domain comment inconsistency (`bolchat.ai` → `bolchat.tech`)
- [ ] Create `/public/og-image.png` (1200×630) — required for social + GSC rich results
- [ ] Add canonical metadata to every `page.tsx` (pricing, features, blog, docs, contact, demo)
- [ ] Add GSC verification code to `layout.tsx`
- [ ] Submit fresh sitemap in Google Search Console
- [ ] Request indexing for homepage, pricing, features, demo, contact manually in GSC
- [ ] Add FAQ JSON-LD schema to homepage
- [ ] Ensure all blog URLs in sitemap have real content (min. 800 words) or remove them

**Content (Week 2–4):**
- [ ] Publish 2 high-quality blog posts (target: "AI agent for website" + "multilingual customer support chatbot")
- [ ] Flesh out all 5 existing blog stubs to min. 800 words each with internal links and CTAs
- [ ] Create `/integrations` page with real content (not a placeholder)
- [ ] Create `/demo` page with a proper booking embed (Calendly or similar)

**Authority Building (Month 1):**
- [ ] Submit to Crunchbase, Product Hunt, G2, Capterra, SaaSHub, BetaList, Indie Hackers
- [ ] Create LinkedIn Company Page + post 3 product updates
- [ ] Post Product Hunt launch (get 200+ upvotes for DA link + brand mentions)

**Search Console Actions:**
- Submit sitemap
- Request indexing for all key pages manually (URL Inspection tool)
- Check Core Web Vitals report — fix any "Poor" URLs

